410", "bbox": [735.3, 799.0, 771.9, 819.9]}, {"text": "177", "bbox": [888.1, 799.0, 924.7, 819.9]}, {"text": "43", "bbox": [1004.3, 799.0, 1025.2, 819.9]}, {"text": "Middle East/Asia", "bbox": [233.3, 826.2, 384.2, 847.1]}, {"text": "510", "bbox": [594.8, 826.2, 631.3, 847.1]}, {"text": "340", "bbox": [735.4, 826.2, 772.0, 847.1]}, {"text": "170", "bbox": [888.2, 826.2, 924.8, 847.1]}, {"text": "50", "bbox": [1004.4, 826.2, 1025.3, 847.1]}, {"text": "Note 1 –", "bbox": [186.7, 852.5, 253.5, 869.1]}, {"text": "All periods presented reflect the new segment structure and the reclassification of certain amounts between the", "bbox": [290.8, 852.5, 1033.7, 869.1]}, {"text": "segments/regions and “Corporate and other.”", "bbox": [290.8, 871.7, 591.4, 888.3]}, {"text": "The increase in consolidated revenue in 2006 compared to 2005 predominantly resulted from increased", "bbox": [215.8, 923.5, 1081.8, 944.4]}, {"text": "activity, higher utilization of our equipment, and increased pricing due to higher exploration and production", "bbox": [140.7, 950.6, 1045.5, 971.5]}, {"text": "spending by our customers.  Revenue in 2005 was impacted by an estimated $80 million in lost revenue due to Gulf", "bbox": [140.7, 977.6, 1112.6, 998.5]}, {"text": "of Mexico hurricanes.  International revenue was 55% of consolidated revenue in 2006 and 57% of consolidated", "bbox": [140.7, 1004.7, 1083.3, 1025.6]}, {"text": "revenue in 2005.", "bbox": [140.7, 1031.9, 285.6, 1052.7]}, {"text": "The increase in consolidated operating income was primarily due to improved demand due to increased rig", "bbox": [215.8, 1058.9, 1112.1, 1079.8]}, {"text": "activity and improved pricing and asset utilization.  Operating income for 2006 included a $48 million gain on the", "bbox": [140.7, 1086.0, 1097.9, 1106.9]}, {"text": "sale of lift boats in west Africa and the North Sea and $47 million of insurance proceeds for business interruptions", "bbox": [140.7, 1113.2, 1100.1, 1134.0]}, {"text": "resulting from the 2005 Gulf of Mexico hurricanes.  Operating income in 2005 was adversely impacted by an", "bbox": [140.7, 1140.2, 1058.0, 1161.0]}, {"text": "estimated $45 million due to Gulf of Mexico hurricanes.", "bbox": [140.7, 1167.3, 616.7, 1188.2]}, {"text": "Following is a discussion of our results of operations by reportable segment.", "bbox": [215.8, 1194.4, 857.4, 1215.3]}]}